{"tid":2492090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Dr. Peter Navarro: 最簡單的解釋也是最正確的解釋是 —— 武漢肺炎來自武漢實驗室","createTime":"2021-04-16T23:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T15:45:01.000Z","uid":226955,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"28f3d8a6a3df213fb1a3016dd93ab1f184589cb6","tid":2492090,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:08:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://amp.washingtontimes.com/news/2021/apr/13/is-dr-fauci-the-father-of-the-pandemic/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Famp.washingtontimes.com%2Fnews%2F2021%2Fapr%2F13%2Fis-dr-fauci-the-father-of-the-pandemic%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=c35f7fc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://amp.washingtontimes.com/news/2021/apr/13/is-dr-fauci-the-father-of-the-pandemic/</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>There is also the logic of Occam&rsquo;s razor: If a deadly virus pops up within several kilometers of the only bio-weapons lab in Asia, the simplest explanation, according to Occam&rsquo;s razor, is usually the right one. Ergo, SARS-CoV-2 came from the Wuhan Lab.</blockquote>"},{"pid":"afbc06c5a5241054f705bdd9f0fe52dc5133d8ff","tid":2492090,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:08:55.000Z","msg":"點解佢會知？？"},{"pid":"f3fd3449a6ba17e0a743c16c5dbdf7bed5bdcdc5","tid":2492090,"uid":226955,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"afbc06c5a5241054f705bdd9f0fe52dc5133d8ff","tid":2492090,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:08:55.000Z","msg":"點解佢會知？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:11:50.000Z","msg":"推敲，但好合理<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>The wet market theory has recent historical precedent. China&rsquo;s first SARS virus, SARS-CoV-1, was quickly tracked to an almost identical virus found in raccoon dogs and Himalayan palm civet cats eaten in wet markets.<br />\n<br />\nYet after testing thousands of animals, no virologist has found a similar &ldquo;direct progenitor&rdquo; of China&rsquo;s second SARS virus. It is therefore extremely unlikely SARS-CoV-2 came from the Wuhan wet market. That leaves the competing Wuhan Lab theory.<br />\n<br />\nWith a biosafety rating of &ldquo;P4,&rdquo; the Wuhan Virology Lab houses the most dangerous pathogens on Earth, including the deadly Ebola. However, no P4 lab is ever 100% secure as there are numerous examples of pathogens escaping.<br />\n<br />\nAn accidental release of SARS-CoV-2 from the Wuhan Lab is therefore well within reason. This is particularly plausible given a U.S. State Department 2018 warning of sloppy safety precautions at the Wuhan Lab and the possibility of a &ldquo;new SARS-like pandemic.&rdquo; (You can&rsquo;t say we weren&rsquo;t warned.)</blockquote>"},{"pid":"db0c3fd33d8fbfa5f376134f0465e6b4d8b1bfd9","tid":2492090,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06aed9e8ccf971583d7a839aea902951a04e5b1d","tid":2492090,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162260af39c5d0a20d944373962f51d1f7a36b8f","tid":2492090,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:15:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"510b8e6138bfec3c88ce8dfa8765e46e4a95bfad","tid":2492090,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ec83f9c3afb727c6f7b213da2d7c0e154f985c","tid":2492090,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9479cb88a12d2613ae56bca944f2b396ab511654","tid":2492090,"uid":294518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:46:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/xi_GLB/status/1382652288544563204?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fxi_GLB%2Fstatus%2F1382652288544563204%3Fs%3D20&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=f1f9f20e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fxi_GLB%2Fstatus%2F1382652288544563204%3Fs%3D20&h=7a338395\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/xi_GLB/status/1382652288544563204?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"0bef2e1670473eebf32c7500fe8784283c37d994","tid":2492090,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d53508cb669b65ff77d789ec276ca58df80ee23","tid":2492090,"uid":238370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"afbc06c5a5241054f705bdd9f0fe52dc5133d8ff","tid":2492090,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:08:55.000Z","msg":"點解佢會知？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:59:54.000Z","msg":"閻博士咪爆左料囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a937df3ab6b72782bb3d6990b07cff24176dfc72","tid":2492090,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T00:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec73f595bd7f9a4007db98f204548e0bfcb3b56","tid":2492090,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T00:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54622ef72b47927cbfe2ccfd2e3f8c37dde4b31","tid":2492090,"uid":267423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T00:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1418a0b862506ed4ad25741b40977b833620a906","tid":2492090,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T00:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c917c9cc3a10876fe11c6735dad8d66ceaf43b0","tid":2492090,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T01:11:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/himalaya_de/status/1383126436081455106?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhimalaya_de%2Fstatus%2F1383126436081455106%3Fs%3D20&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=8571ae57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhimalaya_de%2Fstatus%2F1383126436081455106%3Fs%3D20&h=063bb526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/himalaya_de/status/1383126436081455106?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"7a28bbae06118337e27131774a4a51c28a892045","tid":2492090,"uid":294518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T01:15:02.000Z","msg":"David Asher再次發佈重磅信息：Covid-19是中共生物武器項目的結果<br />\n<br />\n1）根據1月15日解密的情報信息，武漢的幾個研究機構都參與了多項秘密軍事研究項目，這些研究機構全部由解放軍資助，其中包括武漢病毒研究所。 這些研究與「生物防禦」無關，而更像是進攻性武器研究。<br />\n<br />\n2）「功能增強實驗」是「病毒被武器化」的有力證據。 武漢病毒所的動物實驗記錄證實，SARS-CoV-2的毒力是通過連續傳代（卷積）故意增強的，從而找到最佳的生物武器載體。<br />\n<br />\n3）中共對這些真實情況完全撒謊。 <strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">中共每年在日內瓦的生物武器公約上一再宣佈冠狀病毒不是研究的重點，而武漢病毒所是不進行軍事活動的民用機構。這些謊言已經被揭穿，情報和證據已經坐實。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n結論就是：中共說謊，人民死亡。"},{"pid":"ae77fc326cf3a6508946e437b8991cce2ef98840","tid":2492090,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T01:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d902f98